  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248510/extras/c148d80ac29957501416d853d37b24b1.avif?t=1596612658\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>Performer is a game with fun puzzles. Test your logic and ingenuity in different locations of the world as a mercenary who has to eliminate goals or steal secret developments.<br><br>Solve logic tasks and get game currency for which you can open new locations or a new look of the main character. Each new location is stylized for a specific topic and contains its own mechanics, tasks. There are 3 main locations: <br><br> - Shop<br> - Office<br> - Space<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248510/extras/dae77d6948c1fc07e4690a72c03a379b.poster.avif?t=1596612658\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248510/extras/dae77d6948c1fc07e4690a72c03a379b.webm?t=1596612658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248510/extras/dae77d6948c1fc07e4690a72c03a379b.mp4?t=1596612658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248510/extras/c148d80ac29957501416d853d37b24b1.avif?t=1596612658\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>Performer is a game with fun puzzles. Test your logic and ingenuity in different locations of the world as a mercenary who has to eliminate goals or steal secret developments.<br><br>Solve logic tasks and get game currency for which you can open new locations or a new look of the main character. Each new location is stylized for a specific topic and contains its own mechanics, tasks. There are 3 main locations: <br><br> - Shop<br> - Office<br> - Space<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248510/extras/dae77d6948c1fc07e4690a72c03a379b.poster.avif?t=1596612658\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248510/extras/dae77d6948c1fc07e4690a72c03a379b.webm?t=1596612658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1248510/extras/dae77d6948c1fc07e4690a72c03a379b.mp4?t=1596612658\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
